descriptionHtml:
New Update. Recreated start to finish. Worked and tweaked CBBE body and tightened armor.  Used the _0 body so the neck seam doesnt show....Aela wears gloves and boots so no major problems will ensue.  Slight clipping in some areas, almost invisible, unless you try and find it.

If you have the old textures from this, you can delete. This wasnt made for the old textures

Added TBBP to Aela The Huntress\' armor. Enjoy the hunt

Body Type: CBBE
Required: TBBP skeleton
